## ðŸ’¼ Common Use Cases

- Automating CRM or lead tracking
- Syncing data between apps (e.g., Airtable â†” Google Sheets)
- Webhook-based API workflows
- Sending notifications (Slack, Discord, Email)
- Daily/weekly report generation
- Scraping, monitoring, and alerting tasks

